posting_body: ['2611 84th Street Ct, Lakewood, WA 98499', 'When is the last time you felt at home?', 'Here at Crown Pointe we make it our priority to give you a wonderful community to enjoy and a home to make memories in.', 'Our community is nestled in the heart of Lakewood, within blocks of Tacoma Mall, Lakewood Towne Center, University of Washington Tacoma, Military Bases, plus easy access to I-5 and HWY 512.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Washers & Dryers in Every Home', 'Microwave & Stove', 'Dual Pane Windows & Doors', 'Cozy Wood Burning Fireplaces', 'Dishwasher & Garbage Disposal System', 'Energy Saving Heat Reflective Ceilings', 'Community Features:', 'Easy Access to Freeways', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Translation Service Available', 'Community Park', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Close to JBLM, Shopping & Dining', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
